<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-12"><a href="#Modalities.2C_concepts.2C_and_methods"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Modalities, concepts, and methods</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-13"><a href="#Logging_postal_mail"><span class="tocnumber">2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Logging postal mail</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-14"><a href="#Wiretapping"><span class="tocnumber">2.2</span> <span class="toctext">Wiretapping</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-15"><a href="#Legal_foundations"><span class="tocnumber">2.2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Legal foundations</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-16"><a href="#Internet_communications"><span class="tocnumber">2.2.2</span> <span class="toctext">Internet communications</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-17"><a href="#Intelligence_apparatus_to_monitor_Americans"><span class="tocnumber">2.2.3</span> <span class="toctext">Intelligence apparatus to monitor Americans</span></a></li>
