<li id="cite_note-142"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-142">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation news">Kelley, Michael (August 27, 2013). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.businessinsider.com/most-nsa-abuses-are-self-reported-2013-8">"Most NSA Abuses Are Self-Reported"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Business_Insider" title="Business Insider">Business Insider</a>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMass+surveillance+in+the+United+States&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael&amp;rft.au=Kelley%2C+Michael&amp;rft.aulast=Kelley&amp;rft.btitle=Most+NSA+Abuses+Are+Self-Reported&amp;rft.date=August+27%2C+2013&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-nsa-abuses-are-self-reported-2013-8&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
